{
  "name": "RPlog_Fashion_Show",
  "title": "A Charity Fashion Show on Corellia",
  "summary": "In the renovated ballroom of the Royale Hotel in Coronet City, the Kubaz designer Zubindi Hakoon stages a Silverwood House of Fashion charity show benefiting blight-stricken refugees of the Arkanis Sector. Among the glittering crowd are the Tarasar family of Caspar, the retired Dr. Lynae Cassius, the flamboyant fashion critic Thurston Unger with his Chrome Court of couture droids, the shadowy Krackor Reincus, the Zeltron chanteuse Quinne Stardust Rose, the Horansi Kasha, and a committee of ARC dignitaries from across the galaxy. After Zubindi's welcome and an appeal for donations, a succession of masquerade-themed models, Eris, Rylo Ken, Vanilla, Amidala, Euphoria, and Cherish, parade gold-accented Ottegan-silk creations down the catwalk, drawing Thurston's theatrical running commentary, Lynae's wardrobe notes, and Quinne's exuberant outbursts. Lynae reconnects briefly with Krackor before he slips out on urgent business. The show closes to a standing ovation, with Thurston redirecting the applause into a heartfelt plea for Arkanis relief before the guests drift toward the after-party and bar.",
